---
title: Gochujang Glazed Veggie Gyozas with Sesame Fries, Crispy Onions and Pickled Slaw Salad
description: Our Gochujang Glazed Veggie Gyozas is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
